summary: An ordinance relating to the improvement of 14th Ave. Southwest from approximately 30 feet south of Southwest Donovan St. to approximately 160 feet north thereof; and from Southwest Sullivan St. to approximately 100 feet north of Southwest Elmgrove St.; and certain other streets, alleys and an easement, by constructing sanitary sewers and otherwise improving the same, Local Improvement District No. 6312, and appropriating money from the Sewer Fund in aid thereof as a loan.
